---
// FinalCTA - Chamada final para ação com urgência
---

<section class="final-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-card reveal">
      <div class="cta-badge">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
          <polyline points="12,6 12,12 16,14"/>
        </svg>
        Oferta por tempo limitado
      </div>

      <h2>Não pare agora!</h2>
      <p>Você já fez a FTL. Garanta o plano completo e continue sua evolução no inglês.</p>

      <div class="offer-reminder">
        <div class="offer-item">
          <span class="offer-value">30</span>
          <span class="offer-label">aulas/mês*</span>
        </div>
        <div class="offer-divider"></div>
        <div class="offer-item">
          <span class="offer-value">R$ 140</span>
          <span class="offer-label">por mês</span>
        </div>
        <div class="offer-divider"></div>
        <div class="offer-item">
          <span class="offer-value">R$ 4,67</span>
          <span class="offer-label">por aula</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="offer-note">*24 tickets bônus válidos nos 3 primeiros meses</p>

      <a
        href="https://qqenglish.com.br/checkout?plan_id=12586"
        class="btn-promo btn-xl"
        data-checkout-link
        data-cta-location="final"
      >
        Ir para o Checkout
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
        </svg>
      </a>

      <p class="cta-disclaimer">
        Checkout rápido, seguro e sem burocracia
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cta-bg"></div>
</section>

<style>
  .final-cta {
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--section-padding) 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a1628 0%, #1a2a42 100%);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 0% 0%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 100% 100%, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-card {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.15);
    color: var(--color-promo-badge);
    border: 1px solid rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-card h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-card > p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .offer-reminder {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .offer-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .offer-value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-promo-cta);
  }

  .offer-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  }

  .offer-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .offer-divider {
      display: none;
    }

    .offer-reminder {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .offer-item {
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      width: 100%;
    }

    .offer-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
  }

  .btn-xl {
    padding: 1.25rem 3rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .cta-disclaimer {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  }

  .offer-note {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-top: -1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>
